devela::all

Struct IntAlloc 

#[repr(transparent)]
pub struct IntAlloc<T>(pub Int<T>);
Expand description

ðŸ™ ðŸŒ This is a wrapper over Int with additional allocating methods.

Tuple FieldsÂ§

Â§0: Int<T>

ImplementationsÂ§

Â§

impl<T> IntAlloc<T>

pub fn new(inner: T) -> IntAlloc<T>

Creates a new IntAlloc instance wrapping the given value.

The returned instance provides access to both allocating integer methods and the underlying non-allocating Int methods through Deref.
